snippet.title: C64 Game - The Hunt for Red October
snippet.description:
One of two games based on the movie. This is the arcade action one, the other one is a simulator.
1990, Grandslam Entertainment Ltd.  
Musicians: Neil Crossley & Allister Brimble  
Programmers: Neil Crossley & Greg Modern
